Title: Faustina
Writer: José Luis Sáenz de Heredia (operetta), José Luis Sáenz de Heredia (screenplay), Johann Wolfgang von Goethe (play)
Actors: María Félix, Fernando Fernán Gómez, Fernando Rey, Elisa Montés
Plot: A conquering woman of love, power, and fame, is challenged by the devil, as he too, wants to conquer all.
